# 12.74 pre-deploy: .grok/config.toml carries an auto-managed Bearer
# token for the shellx-host-http MCP. It rotates per install and must
# never be committed. Also covers grok-build's session caches that
# would otherwise pollute the repo with per-user state.
.grok/
.shellx/

